summary: The code imports the os module and defines a list of commands. It then iterates through each command, executes it using the os.system() function, installing yt-dlp and downloading a YouTube video with its unique link.

details.comment: The code imports the os module and defines a list of commands. It then iterates through each command, executes it using the os.system() function, installing yt-dlp and downloading a YouTube video with its unique link.
details.content:
import os
commands = ["pip3 install yt-dlp",'yt-dlp "https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=FuV63EEhS8c"']
for c in commands:
    os.system(c)
